long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension enables you to run Metal Calculator as a streamlined application within your Chrome browser.

Key Features:

 - Launch Metal Calculator effortlessly with a single click.
 - Access Metal Calculator directly from your browser's toolbar for quick and convenient use.
